name: An Ottoman Painter's Gravestone
description: An Ottoman Painter's Gravestone, Cevad Seyyid Bey Edirne/Turkey  ''Painter and Physician Cevad Seyyid Bey,  who was killed for the sake of his duty  when he was 38 years old.''  ''Otuz sekiz yaşında iken  Vazifesi uğrunda kurban Ve nail-i rahmet-i rahman olan Ressam ve tabib-i hazık Cevad Seyyid…''
